r\nFor questions, contact admin@texaspaceauthority.org\r\n\r\nPhoto Credit: \"<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/usacehq/5056771149/in/photolist-8GRgTt-9GzLgu-9A9WT9-9HEdHK-ayZJhh-9VTAzN-apamtg-7VdRWo-9XJcec-9Gx3AT-ewVayZ-aoWWxA-ayX5D6-m8rF6Y-bXPwWL-ewXUuL-bXPx77-8CEaDU-cha7yy-965NsL-7z7a5z-bXMMao-eY8dHe-jF3yxs-9GzRxj-9qPXJ4-9Jz6Q4-ekEBbH-bmvbff-bXN29U-8Vx5ze-8VA7Ab-8Vx5ba-9Jzkxp-qwVfMm-bXMr8S-bXMqHC-6EqX5C-bXMqeY-bXMJ3G-bXMr6b-9ZRAEU-8PjmEZ-9GzUb5-fK1pzx-artr2f-chawmU-cEEZW7-ciLpz7-fxRofL\">Contractors Review Plans</a>\" by <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/usacehq/\">U.S. Army Corps of Engineers</a> is licensed under <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/\">CC BY 2.0</a>', 'Events', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '838-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-11-18 22:40:24', '2015-11-18 22:40:24', '', '838', 'http://www.texaspaceauthority.org/838-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_bcyw_posts` VALUES('843', '6', '2015-11-18 22:41:07', '2015-11-18 22:41:07', '<strong>Events and Training</strong>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nAre you an engineer or contractor providing energy and water efficiency building technologies? Do you want to be a service provider in Texas\' PACE ecosystem?\r\n\r\nIf so, Texas PACE Authority would like to invite you to attend our PACE Training Workshop\r\n\r\nThe purpose of this Training will be to discuss in detail how to complete a PACE project from start to finish, and how it can be helpful for you and Texas\' property owners. Topics of discussion will include:\r\n\r\n\"How to Market PACE\"\r\n\"Technical Standards for a Project\"\r\n\"The Application Process\"\r\n\"Available Commercial Rebates\"\r\n\"Financial Modeling of PACE Projects\"\r\nAttendees will receive lunch, a binder with printed materials including advocacy and application documents, and a USB drive containing all digital files. The cost of attendance is $75, and will cover the aforementioned lunch, binder, USB drive, and Training.\r\n\r\nAny service provider who completes a PACE Training workshop will gain access to the USGBC Marketplace listings under the PACE category.\r\n\r\nSign ups can be found per location at the following links:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nCentral Texas\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/e/austin-pace-service-provider-training-january-22nd-2016-tickets-19537333691\">https://www.eventbrite.com/e/pace-service-provider-training-january-22nd-2016-tickets-19537333691</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nGulf Coast\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/e/houston-pace-service-provider-training-february-25th-2016-tickets-19628194458\">https://www.eventbrite.com/e/houston-pace-service-provider-training-february-25th-2016-tickets-19628194458</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWebinars\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nThe Texas PACE Authority has no upcoming webinars yet.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFor questions, contact admin@texaspaceauthority.org\r\n\r\nPhoto Credit: \"<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/usacehq/5056771149/in/photolist-8GRgTt-9GzLgu-9A9WT9-9HEdHK-ayZJhh-9VTAzN-apamtg-7VdRWo-9XJcec-9Gx3AT-ewVayZ-aoWWxA-ayX5D6-m8rF6Y-bXPwWL-ewXUuL-bXPx77-8CEaDU-cha7yy-965NsL-7z7a5z-bXMMao-eY8dHe-jF3yxs-9GzRxj-9qPXJ4-9Jz6Q4-ekEBbH-bmvbff-bXN29U-8Vx5ze-8VA7Ab-8Vx5ba-9Jzkxp-qwVfMm-bXMr8S-bXMqHC-6EqX5C-bXMqeY-bXMJ3G-bXMr6b-9ZRAEU-8PjmEZ-9GzUb5-fK1pzx-artr2f-chawmU-cEEZW7-ciLpz7-fxRofL\">Contractors Review Plans</a>\" by <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/usacehq/\">U.S. Army Corps of Engineers</a> is licensed under <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/\">CC BY 2.0</a>', 'Events', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '838-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-11-18 22:41:07', '2015-11-18 22:41:07', '', '838', 'http://www.texaspaceauthority.org/838-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
